"DATA","HS_S_37_DCPT","SCP","FINAL","662559.00","6243297.20","","-28.29","HS_S_37_DCPT was completed to a final recovered depth of 29.14m.  The borehole was progressed with CPTU testing utilising 1m, 2.5m and 3m Wison tools with 5cm and 10cm cones and API drilling techniques. The borehole was completed in agreement with OCR due to SBF sinkage >1.00m.","29.14","2023-09-02 00:00:00","RECONNAISSANCE","","2023-09-02 00:00:00","HEW02","GTR","GL1","GARDLINE","GRS 1980","UTM Zone 32N","ETRS89","25832","MSL","5715","2023-09-02 00:00:00","Echosounder","M.V. Kommandor Susan"
"DATA","HS_S_38_BH","EH","FINAL","659178.20","6243041.40","","-20.98","HS_S _38_BH was completed from mudline to a final penetrated depth of 70.30m and a final recovered depth of 70.13m. The borehole was advanced with alternating CPT and downhole sampling from mudline utilising API drilling and PQ3 coring techniques. Upon completion of the sampling operations P-S logging data was obtained from 70m to 5m below mudline.","70.30","2023-09-11 00:00:00","RECONNAISSANCE","","2023-09-14 00:00:00","HEW02","GTR","GL1","GARDLINE","GRS 1980","UTM Zone 32N","ETRS89","25832","MSL","5715","2023-09-11 00:00:00","Echosounder","M.V. Kommandor Susan"
"DATA","HS_S_39_CPT","SCP","FINAL","656919.90","6242688.20","","-18.70","HS_S_39_CPT was completed to a final recovered depth of 5.8m. The test was terminated due to total load reached. The SBF had a recorded sinkage of 0.10m Test returned Class 1 data.","5.80","2023-04-06 00:00:00","RECONNAISSANCE","","2023-04-06 00:00:00","HEW02","GTR","GL1","GARDLINE","GRS 1980","UTM Zone 32N","ETRS89","25832","MSL","5715","2023-04-06 00:00:00","Echosounder","M.V. Kommandor Susan"
"DATA","HS_S_39_CPT_A","SCP","FINAL","656922.20","6242692.30","","-18.70","HS_S_39_CPT_A was completed to a final recovered depth of 6.74m. The test was terminated due to total load reached. The SBF had a recorded sinkage of 0.10m Test returned Class 1 data.","6.74","2023-04-06 00:00:00","RECONNAISSANCE","","2023-04-06 00:00:00","HEW02","GTR","GL1","GARDLINE","GRS 1980","UTM Zone 32N","ETRS89","25832","MSL","5715","2023-04-06 00:00:00","Echosounder","M.V. Kommandor Susan"
"DATA","HS_S_39_DCPT_A","SCP","FINAL","656918.00","6242684.40","","-19.25","HS_S_39_DCPT_A was completed to a final recovered depth of 30.10m.  The borehole was progressed with CPTU testing utilising 1m and 2.5m Wison tools with 5cm and 10cm cones. The borehole was advanced using API drilling techniques.","30.10","2023-08-28 00:00:00","RECONNAISSANCE","","2023-08-29 00:00:00","HEW02","GTR","GL1","GARDLINE","GRS 1980","UTM Zone 32N","ETRS89","25832","MSL","5715","2023-08-28 00:00:00","Echosounder","M.V. Kommandor Susan"

